    "AI-based inference engines can transform X-ray equipment into valuable testing equipment for diagnosing COVID-19 using specified DL methods.",
    "In contrast to earlier research in the area, inference engines were constructed from the ground up, utilizing novel deep neural networks and no preexisting systems.",
    "COV19-CNNet and COV19-ResNet are the two engine designations.",
